Script commands
-------------------------

(battle commands)
------------------
ismob(#) - returns 0 if not a monster, 1 if is.  # can be any number
paralyze # - set to 2 if paralyze, 1 if blind.  -2 to take off para, -1 to take off blind
setrage # - Sets rage(aka Cunning, Fury) to the modifier.(#=modifier)
setbackstab # - #=1:Backstab on, #=0:Backstab off
setflank # - same as above

(npc commands)
